{"tid":1471082,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"神秘撞船！貨輪撞掉中國艦武器系統　台軍如獲至寶　中國封口不提","createTime":"2019-08-14T07:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T10:38:44.000Z","uid":35519,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5253cae199b95ef0405ac9a3fc6ff39e2f51e0a2","tid":1471082,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:42:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">貨輪撞掉陸艦武器系統　台軍如獲至寶</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-08-14/900/20190814001988.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-08-14%2F900%2F20190814001988.jpg&h=d0fe6304&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>台貨輪撞掉陸艦飛彈護衛艦重要武器系統，掉落在甲板上遭台方帶回調查。</em><br />\n<br />\n金門料羅灣東南外海上月(31日〉晚間，發生一起我國籍貨輪與大陸軍艦擦撞的神祕撞船事件，因過於敏感，兩岸至今都封口不提，本刊掌握獨家訊息，這起撞船事件中，我方竟意外獲得重大收穫。據了解，大陸軍艦上一具搜索雷達系統，另有一說是射控系統竟被撞飛，掉落在「友泰一號」甲板上，讓我軍方如獲至寶，也據此判斷出陸艦的型號，可說是天上掉下來的禮物，也顯見當時撞擊力道之大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-01-22/900/20180122003864.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-01-22%2F900%2F20180122003864.jpg&h=afc8d1cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>隸屬中國東海艦隊的056A型輕護衛艦銅仁艦2016年2月20日已入列，具有強大的防空，反潛與對海作戰能力。</em><br />\n<br />\n這起撞船因過於敏感，兩岸至今仍不願透露撞船細節與軍艦型號，大陸軍方至今不敢透過民間海事糾紛進行調查，整起事故猶如石沉大海。<br />\n<br />\n當時本報第一時間獨家掌握貨船撞上的是陸艦，而且可能是噸位僅次於遼寧號航母，大陸最新071型船塢登陸艦「龍虎山號」，也可能為不知名飛彈護衛艦。<strong><ins>因事涉機密敏感，陸方目前完全不提，我軍方與國安系統也保持沉默。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>本報掌握，事件當晚「友泰一號」返回金門料羅港接受調查時，我方人員竟<ins>在貨輪前甲板上，發現一具「不知名大型儀器」</ins>，一看就是軍艦上的裝備，我方人員不敢大意，立刻通報軍方派員前往查看，<ins>到場人員檢視該具儀器後臉色大驚</ins>，立刻迅速封裝帶離現場，並要求所有人員封口。</strong><br />\n<br />\n當時傳出，大陸軍艦掉落的是一個極機密裝備，軍方內部一度盛傳是短程飛彈發射器，甚至是魚雷發射管。<strong><ins>不過本報掌握，由軍方人員帶回的該具極敏感裝備，疑是一具光電搜索雷達或是火砲射控雷達。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n根據判斷，<strong><ins>該具雷達系統，目前應該是裝設在大陸056A型最新飛彈護衛艦，是大陸海軍主要的海軍基地防衛艦艇</ins></strong>，噸位約1400噸，與「友泰一號」貨輪大小相當。艦上武裝包括鷹擊83反艦飛彈、紅旗-10防空飛彈及俄製76艦砲，30釐米遙控艦砲等，火力相當強大。<br />\n<br />\n至於掉落在「友泰一號」的裝備到底是屬於哪一型武器系統裝備系統，目前相關單位軍守口如瓶，不願意證實，僅稱是「非常機敏」的裝備。<br />\n<br />\n軍方獲得這個意外的禮物，也讓軍方證實了，當時「友泰一號」撞上並非的是傳聞中的「龍虎山號」，而是當時擔任護衛艦的056A型飛彈護衛艦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190814001933-260407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20190814001933-260407&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3a%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=a8dc3534\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190814001933-260407</a>"},{"pid":"f15c9ea6f5e084f397774173670c503c752f5e69","tid":1471082,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"077e87869f9976b1c1033c1f08b26dd69df33e22","tid":1471082,"uid":174541,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:44:31.000Z","msg":"禮貌版<br />\n前線你好！核彈我也不會割。天琦說過與港共鬥爭不能有任何底線。既然有鬼捉不了已成事實(亦得到官方承認)，何不反其道而行，將一切大眾不能接受的行為推卸給popo(注意！並非割！)有了這免死金牌，前線能放下民意顧慮，盡情去做該做的事(不要斷正就可以)。你們的背後有我們！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">誠狠版<br />\n屌你老母，醒少少好唔好?班差佬畀咗咁大 個核彈你都唔識玩?！ 天琦講過你班撚屌唔好有任何潔癖， 咁撚正氣點打中共啲陰招。示威肯定有鬼， 捉嚟都嘥鳩氣。 用下你個豬腦逆向思維咁諗， 有咩事咪奶撚落曬啲臥底到囉。 大眾淨係需要一個合理到嘅版本，陰謀論冇所謂㗎。 拎撚住依個免死金牌， 前線手足咪可以放手做，文宣我哋咪可以輕鬆打囉。 屌你老母，對面元朗嗰時已經做緊謠，唔係唔撚返佢哋呀?</span></span>"},{"pid":"0e860235e7a6f2f8886f7d73bc0052d1fafa77d7","tid":1471082,"uid":35519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:45:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://disp.cc/b/163-bBVs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdisp.cc%2Fb%2F163-bBVs&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3a%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=61bb015c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://disp.cc/b/163-bBVs</a><br />\n<br />\nv21638245: 笑死<br />\nzz71: 護國貨輪<br />\nASHOCK: 蔡英文撿到雷達  XDDDD<br />\ndarky897: 中台友好<br />\npp9960: 逆向工程軍方也懂<br />\ndistress0730: 這年頭連雷達都能撿<br />\nbicedb: 要求所有人員封口。 然後記者<br />\nhong414: 撞一下就掉下來 渣... 偉大的中國 哈<br />\nekoj: XDD 幹 封口還爆出來...中國臉往哪擺？<br />\nas2s2ss2s: 打王本來就有寶可以撿<br />\nlegos4710: 打怪打到掉紫裝 笑死XDDDDDDD<br />\nArietta: 唬爛啊 撞一下就掉設備，戰艦這麼脆弱？<br />\nIN945: 五毛氣到噴汁，自己的納稅錢被軍方貪污光了，連儀器都能被撞飛XD"},{"pid":"2ea346dfa5e2e39e0c9d6a20cedb3cee4bd610b1","tid":1471082,"uid":35519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:48:22.000Z","msg":"pchunters123: 掉裝備的概念<br />\nyafx4200p: 撞一下就掉...還不討回 還真他媽的弱<br />\nlegendmtg: 真的假的啦 也太爽了吧XDDDD<br />\nSummer1308: 要求封口然後證實是護衛艦XD<br />\nchunglee: 噗哈哈哈哈，隨便一艘魚船屌打支那軍艦<br />\nMIN945: 五毛真的超生氣耶，怎樣，解放軍比台灣貨輪還廢，被撞到噴裝後只會抱頭鼠竄XD<br />\nchunglee: 這新聞前陣子有啊，當時有說海巡去追，對方低調一直跑，後來趕上時有廣播說海巡要登船，協商雙方賠償事宜，對方因為船受損說不用了要趕回去處理。原來是被撞掉了雷達哈哈<br />\nseastar1982: 完了 艦長要去北大荒了<br />\nkenndy: 豆腐渣軍艦嗎？漁船一撞就掉<br />\nkillla: 謝丞相箭？"},{"pid":"eeff2ab71cf38291ef21acbdd0d784de04058c4b","tid":1471082,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:50:21.000Z","msg":"又會咁o岩掉落到甲板<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪無錢到要賣爛鐵？"},{"pid":"53e6b980b0923b8f08af7460506dcffb08b3d514","tid":1471082,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UWs0pSY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUWs0pSY.gif&h=677ca997&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6609b663c121adbea724beb897d778816cf13d90","tid":1471082,"uid":249480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:52:03.000Z","msg":"大陸隻垃圾分分鐘沈左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05093ed0f38f8e9d976b414b2ae2cec2a4a62b38","tid":1471082,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:04:32.000Z","msg":"偉大中國的航母<br />\n美軍見到黑煙已經嚇到噴屎<br />\n<img src=\"https://d262ilb51hltx0.cloudfront.net/max/1287/1*CyCAtRXYw9Y2xyXA4ay0aQ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd262ilb51hltx0.cloudfront.net%2Fmax%2F1287%2F1%2ACyCAtRXYw9Y2xyXA4ay0aQ.jpeg&h=52676be6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以解放軍為榮<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/25/153939_c1d8ff99252c6946084bc07d7690e85b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F153939_c1d8ff99252c6946084bc07d7690e85b.jpg&h=eb020c28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對比戰鬥力只有5既美軍<br />\n<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/pop.h-cdn.co/assets/16/23/1465497327-otago.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fpop.h-cdn.co%2Fassets%2F16%2F23%2F1465497327-otago.gif&h=27eacae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://special-ops.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/us-navy-seals-buds-770x496.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspecial-ops.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2Fus-navy-seals-buds-770x496.jpg&h=de61c5e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"464fe32cf98826cfbff1e1acf41ea23b53024605","tid":1471082,"uid":193436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:38:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}